title: THE MAJORA'S MASK ICEBERG: A Deep Dive into a Parallel World

media:group.media:title: THE MAJORA'S MASK ICEBERG: A Deep Dive into a Parallel World
media:group.media:description:
Well, here we are, back again with another Legend of Zelda iceberg video. We'll be specifically looking at Majora's Mask, a beautifully complex and emotional experience based in the intertwining world of Termina, an alternate world to Hyrule. I’ll be covering every entry on this Majora’s Mask iceberg chart from the top to the bottom, with entries near the top being more well known, and entries near the bottom being less known and generally a bit spookier.
